import React from 'react'
import { observer } from "mobx-react-lite";
import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container'
import Nav from 'react-bootstrap/Nav'
import Navbar from 'react-bootstrap/Navbar'
import NavDropdown from 'react-bootstrap/NavDropdown'
import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button'

const AppSetting = observer(({ grid, animation }) => {
    return (
        <Navbar className='app-setting'>
            <Container>
                <NavDropdown title='Algorithm'>
                    <NavDropdown.Item>A* Search</NavDropdown.Item>
                    <NavDropdown.Item>Bidirectional Swarm Algorithm</NavDropdown.Item>
                    <NavDropdown.Item>Breadth First Search</NavDropdown.Item>
                    <NavDropdown.Item>Convergent Swarm Algorithm</NavDropdown.Item>
                    <NavDropdown.Item>Depth First Search</NavDropdown.Item>
                    <NavDropdown.Item onClick={() => animation.setAlgorithm("dfs")}>Dijkstra</NavDropdown.Item>
                    <NavDropdown.Item>Greedy Best-first Search</NavDropdown.Item>
                    <NavDropdown.Item>Swarm Algorithm</NavDropdown.Item>
                </NavDropdown>
                <select>
                    <option value="bfs" onChange={value => animation.setAlgorithm("bfs")}>Breadth First Search</option>
                    <option value="dfs" onChange={value => animation.setAlgorithm("dfs")}>Depth First Search</option>
                </select>
                <NavDropdown title='Mazes & Patterns'>
                    <NavDropdown.Item>Basic Random Maze</NavDropdown.Item>
                    <NavDropdown.Item>Basic Weighted Maze</NavDropdown.Item>
                    <NavDropdown.Item>Recursive Division</NavDropdown.Item>
                    <NavDropdown.Item>Recursive Division (vertical skew)</NavDropdown.Item>
                    <NavDropdown.Item>Recursive Division (horizontal skew)</NavDropdown.Item>
                    <NavDropdown.Item>Simple Stair Pattern</NavDropdown.Item>
                </NavDropdown>
                <NavDropdown title='Speed'>
                    <NavDropdown.Item>Fast</NavDropdown.Item>
                    <NavDropdown.Item>Average</NavDropdown.Item>
                    <NavDropdown.Item>Slow</NavDropdown.Item>
                </NavDropdown>
            </Container>
        </Navbar>
    )
})

export default AppSetting
